Class ObjectCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • editor.ObjectCollection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Matrix, Vector

    public class ObjectCollection
extends java.lang.Object

    OBJECTCOLLECTION

    Class that is the parent class of Vector and Matrix classes and that contains their maxDimenion attribute and methods getter and setter related to this. It is used to set up the template where the matrices and vectors are going to be embeded.
